=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /'gɪni pɪɡ/

=== Noun ===

'''guinea pig'''

#a small [[mammal]] with short [[ear]]s and short [[tail]], often kept by people as a [[pet]], bigger than a [[hamster]].
#a [[rodent]] used in laboratory [[experiment]]s. Also a [[person]] used in the same manner.
#a person who is a first on a particular program, etc.

